      "body": "Morning,\n\n\n\nIs your systems working ok?\n\n\n\nIt’s not loading\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/z0NZ301MeiePkOGVH1W1MizA6/?name=image001.png)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/cBF58aeqaUhlUczL9Vws0vSsc/?name=image002.png)\n\n\n\n**From:** Manohar V (PluginHive) <support@pluginhive.com>\n**Sent:** Tuesday, 10 March 2026 6:45 AM\n**To:** Tony Vo <tony@saintfelix.com.au>\n**Subject:** [PluginHive] Re: Can you help me set up live rate calculations on ...\n\n\n\nYour request (377536) has been updated. To add additional comments, reply to this email.\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/system/photos/9996081007001/PHOTO.jpeg)\n\n**Manohar V** (PluginHive)\n\nMar 10, 2026, 01:14 GMT+5:30\n\nHello Tony Vo,\n\nThank you for your reply.\n\nYes, your understanding is correct. You can update the **carrier service names** by navigating to**App → Settings → Shipping Rates → Carrier Services**.\n\nPlease feel free to reach out to us anytime if you need any assistance from our end. We will be happy to help.\n\nThanks and Regards,\nManohar V\nTeam PluginHive\n\n\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/images/2016/default-avatar-80.png)\n\n**Tony Vo**\n\nMar 10, 2026, 00:45 GMT+5:30\n\nThankyou, working!\n\n\n\nHow do I update the names below?\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/rx7jVOgxCmnrrtadVnzpzXsnM/?name=image001.png)\n\n\n\n\n\nIs it in this section below?\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/NcAlaW3M8NkRkPrCtVDYwTyn6/?name=image002.png)\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/t9FJHmoenToLxkl73m5MMpxjX/?name=image003.png)\n\n\n\n\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/system/photos/10479726420761/Image_-_Sagar.jpg)\n\n**Sagar K S** (PluginHive)\n\nMar 7, 2026, 05:48 GMT+5:30\n\nHello Tony\n\nThank you for your response.\n\nWhen checking for the rates at the checkout, complete shipping address details have to be provided for the rates to be shown from both the carriers.\n\nIn your case, it looks like the City/Suburb was not provided and the Aramex was not able to calculate rates.\n\nI have added a product to the cart, provided complete shipping details and both Aramex and Au Post rates are provided.\n\nPlease check and confirm.\n\n ![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/attachments/token/NPD1Xw4UVbN0j3JMlt2YzWdCW/?name=image.png)\n\nBest regards,\nSagar K S\nPluginHive\n\n\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/images/2016/default-avatar-80.png)\n\n**Tony Vo**\n\nMar 7, 2026, 05:02 GMT+5:30\n\nThanks\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/J5qoKTY8344Klzzq8tX2CshsE/?name=image001.png)\n\n\n\nIt isn’t coming up with Aramex, only Australia post at the moment.\n\n\n\n![](https://support.pluginhive.com/attachments/token/Ri7iD0JT5BhxvyoLXMg3YDiVz/?name=image002.png)\n\n\n\n\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/system/photos/10479726420761/Image_-_Sagar.jpg)\n\n**Sagar K S** (PluginHive)\n\nMar 7, 2026, 03:36 GMT+5:30\n\nHello Tony,\n\nGreetings from PluginHive!\n\nWe could see that the app was not registered to show shipping rates at the checkout.\n\nI have registered the app with the store now. Could you please add a product to the cart and check for the rates?\n\nBest regards,\nSagar K S\nPluginHive\n\n\n\n![](https://pluginhive.zendesk.com/images/2016/default-avatar-80.png)\n\n**Tony Vo**\n\nMar 7, 2026, 03:13 GMT+5:30\n\nCan you help me set up live rate calculations on shopify? when i go in the shopify shipping zone - i cant see the PH Multi carrier shipping label\n\n------------------\nSubmitted from: https://mcsl-s.pluginhive.io/home/settings/shipper/shippingzones/rule/new\n\n![PluginHive](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/pluginhive_logo.png)\n\n**Our Support is available 24/5.**\n\nPlease expect a delay during weekends & holidays due to partial coverage.\n\nDocumentation**|**\n\nVideos**|**\n\nWooCommerce Plugins**|**\n\nShopify Apps**|**\n\nMagento Extensions\n\n![ph-facebook](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PH-facebook.png) ![ph-linkedin](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PH-linkedin.png) ![ph-twitter](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PH-twitter.png) ![ph-youtube](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PH-youtube.png) ![ph-twitter](https://www.pluginhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PH-instagram.png)\n\n[VE3WXV-DLENL]",
